    "name": "Hubert",
    "epitet": "Sinister Servant",
    "display": "Hubert: Sinister Servant",
    "description": "The Adrestian Empire's Minister of the Imperial Household and legitimate son of Marquis Vestra. Has sworn complete fealty to Edelgard. Appears in Fire Emblem: Three Houses.",
    "artist": "PenekoR (п猫Ｒ)",
    "voiceActorEN": "Robbie Daymond",
    "voiceActorJP": "小西克幸",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I am Hubert, heir to House Vestra and future minister to the emperor. Pleased to make your acquaintance.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "A big family of Heroes, caring and watching out for one another. How nauseating.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I am Lady Edelgard's humble servant. I serve you for now, but my true loyalties lie with her. Don't forget it.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You like watching from afar as others spill blood on your behalf. You and the goddess have that in common.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Some say I'm a rat—always conniving in the shadows. Perhaps so. But I'm not the only rat around here.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I have been analyzing the enemy's weak points so we can exploit them. I will give you a report shortly.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I come bearing well wishes on your friend's behalf. Please tell your friend I have more important things to do.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "Any experience is worth having.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "This strength will serve Lady Edelgard well!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "This is harder than expected.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Heh, this suits me well.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "You have a useful talent for expelling enemies from the world of the living. I find it charming. Provided you held no ill will toward Lady Edelgard, I would consider inviting you to join me in the Empire. Of course, I cannot allow a personal attachment to compromise my devotion to Lady Edelgard. I am sworn eternally and irrevocably to her service. However... If there existed a version of me who had never thus pledged himself, he may have offered his life to you.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
